data.description: This home's mortgage is assumable at around 5.8%! Road was just paved & new curbs installed! This corner lot home is ready for you. Two car attached garage. All appliances stay, including washer & dryer. Lots of storage. Half bath off the laundry room. Concrete patio in the back. Practically no electric bill. Solar panels installed January 2023 and will transfer, including $206 payment, to the new owner. Seller will cover first 24 months of payments after you own the home. Nest thermostat. Big side yard. Schedule your showing today!
